&lt;h1 id=&#34;diffusion-policy-and-flow-matching-foundations&#34;&gt;Diffusion Policy and Flow Matching: Foundations&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This note summarizes the foundations of &lt;strong&gt;diffusion models&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;diffusion policy&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;flow matching&lt;/strong&gt;, with an emphasis on both the formal derivation and the intuition behind them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The central question is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How can a model learn to transform a simple noise distribution into a complex structured data distribution?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
